'''羅渣·莊臣'''（{{lang-en|'''Roger Johnson'''}}，{{bd|1983年|4月28日|catIDx=Johnson, Roger}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[後衛_(足球)|後衛]]，現時效力[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]。

羅渣·莊臣在[[韦康比流浪者足球俱乐部|韋甘比]]開展足球事業，以[[職業|職業]]球員身份效力6年。他其後加盟[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]，成為勇闖2008年[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]決賽的成員之一，更兩度獲選球會年度最佳球員。2009年他轉投當時還在[[英超|英超]]作賽的球會[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]，效力兩季於球會降班後轉投[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]。

==生平==
===球會===
====韋甘比====
羅渣·莊臣早年曾參加[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]及[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|般尼茅夫]]的足球訓練，於15歲加入[[韦康比流浪者足球俱乐部|韋甘比]]青訓系統，在1999/2000年球季閉幕日為一隊首次上陣出戰[[剑桥联足球俱乐部|劍橋聯]]，成為當時球會最年青的聯賽上陣球員，年僅17歲零8日。翌季羅渣·莊臣僅於對[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]取得1次後補上陣機會。2001/02年球季由於球隊傷兵問題嚴重，時任領隊[[劳瑞·桑切斯|劳瑞·桑切斯]]（Lawrie Sanchez）派遣羅渣·莊臣上陣7場聯賽，並在對[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]取得首個入球，韋甘比隨即提供三年新約予羅渣·莊臣，但他不幸因傷提早結束球季。2002/03年球季羅渣·莊臣為球隊在各項賽事合共上陣35場及射入3球。2003/04年球季在領隊[[托尼·亚当斯|托尼·亚当斯]]麾下雖然未能站穩正選席位，但仍獲球迷選為「年度最佳球員」（Fans' Player of the Year）<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.chairboys.ndirect.co.uk/players/johnson_roger.htm |title=Roger Johnson |publisher=''chairboys.net'' |accessdate=30 January 2009 |archive-date=2019-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819143526/http://www.chairboys.ndirect.co.uk/players/johnson_roger.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

托尼·亚当斯僅任教一季後便離隊，羅渣·莊臣成為球隊當然正選，更獲於2004年11月上任的領隊[[约翰·高曼|约翰·高曼]]（John Gorman）委任為[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]，並於12月續約至2007年夏季。

====卡迪夫城====
2006年7月4日羅渣·莊臣於為[[韦康比流浪者足球俱乐部|韋甘比]]上陣182場及射入22球後，以27萬5,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉投[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]，雖然其南[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]敵對球隊[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]亦對羅渣·莊臣有意，但其10萬英鎊出價被韋甘比拒絕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5144478.stm |title=Cardiff beat Swansea to Johnson |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=4 July 2006 |accessdate=29 December 2009 |archive-date=2006-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060707031830/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5144478.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

羅渣·莊臣於加盟頭半季主要擔任後補球員，其後與[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]外援[[格連·盧雲斯|格連·盧雲斯]]（Glenn Loovens）組成穩固的中路拍檔，使[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]][[达伦·普尔斯|达伦·普尔斯]]（Darren Purse）無路請纓。2007/08年球季羅渣·莊臣更經常取得入球，於對[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]的聯賽末段射入致勝球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6963672.stm |title=Norwich 1 – 2 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=1 September 2007 |accessdate=1 September 2007}}</ref>，而對[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]的[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第一圈更在[[加時賽|加時賽]]才射入唯一入球淘汰對手<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/6941839.stm |title=Cardiff 1 – 0 Brighton (aet) |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=14 August 2007 |accessdate=14 August 2007 |archive-date=2019-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228033611/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/6941839.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；作客對[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]於完場前為球隊扳平2-2<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7110782.stm |title=Hull 2 – 2 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=1 December 2007 |accessdate=1 December 2007}}</ref>及對[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]再入1球協助球隊最終反勝2-1<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7157326.stm |title=Preston 1 – 2 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=29 December 2007 |accessdate=29 December 2007 |archive-date=2007-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071231085419/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7157326.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。羅渣·莊臣於[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]半準決賽作客對當時尚在[[英超|英超]]的[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]射入，為卡迪夫城鎖定2-0勝局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/7272793.stm |title=Middlesbrough 0 – 2 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=9 March 2008 |accessdate=9 March 2008 |archive-date=2008-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080309230359/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/7272793.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而他在「塞文區打吡」（Severnside Derby）主場頂入[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]大門已是他季內第七個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7298092.stm |title=Cardiff 2 – 1 Bristol City |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-03-22 |accessdate=2011-01-25 |archive-date=2008-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080325005450/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7298092.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於卡迪夫城晉級足總盃決賽過程中的6場賽事羅渣·莊臣全部均有上陣，但在決賽以0-1不敵[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]只能屈居亞席。球季結束後，他獲選球會「年度最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.cardiffcity-mad.co.uk/news/loadnews.asp?cid=TMNW&id=387760 |title=Roger Johnson wins player of the year award |publisher=''cardiffcity-mad.co.uk'' |date= |accessdate=30 January 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090630134049/http://www.cardiffcity-mad.co.uk/news/loadnews.asp?cid=TMNW&id=387760 |archivedate=2009年6月30日 }}</ref>。

2008年夏季羅渣·莊臣一直與[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]及[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]扯上關係，但兩隊的出價均被卡迪夫城拒絕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7441723.stm |title=Bluebirds reject bids for Johnson |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=10 September 2008 |accessdate=10 September 2008}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7587639.stm |title=Cardiff refuse Ledley Stoke talks |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=10 September 2008 |accessdate=10 September 2008 |archive-date=2008-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080917215554/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7587639.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。新球季展開後羅渣·莊臣仍然留隊，但他的中路拍檔格連·盧雲斯離隊轉投[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:凯尔特人; zh-hk:些路迪;}-]]，於揭幕日主場對[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]，羅渣·莊臣又在完場前為球隊奠定勝局，以2-1的比數旗開得勝。雖然經常轉換拍檔，羅渣·莊臣是陣中唯一於季內踢足全部賽事每一分鐘的球員，更超越為球隊上陣100場的里程碑，直至2009年4月11日作客2-0擊敗[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]，他被對方守將[[克劳德·戴维斯|克劳德·戴维斯]]（Claude Davis）用手肘撞中喉嚨而受傷離場，事後羅渣·莊臣感到呼吸困難而需要留醫兩日，於接下來一星期更要每天接受檢查<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7998668.stm |title=Johnson eager for Cardiff return |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=18 April 2009 |accessdate=18 April 2009 |archive-date=2009-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090417065023/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7998668.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2009/04/17/roger-johnson-on-mend-but-cardiff-city-boss-dave-jones-still-fuming-91466-23403781/ |title=Roger Johnson on mend, but Cardiff City boss Dave Jones still fuming |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=18 April 2009 |accessdate=18 April 2009 |archive-date=2009-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422191342/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2009/04/17/roger-johnson-on-mend-but-cardiff-city-boss-dave-jones-still-fuming-91466-23403781/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後戴维斯因粗暴行為被[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]]判罰停賽三場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/crystal_palace/8000837.stm |title=Davis guilty of violent conduct |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=18 April 2009 |accessdate=18 April 2009 |archive-date=2009-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090418173931/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/crystal_palace/8000837.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。羅渣·莊臣缺席球隊下一場3-1擊敗[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]的賽事，於翌週0-6大敗於[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]腳下復出。4月26日他連續兩年獲選球會「年度最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2009/04/27/roll-of-honour-91466-23478829/ |title=Cardiff City supporters club roll call of honour |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=27 April 2009 |accessdate=27 April 2009}}</ref>，更入選「[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英冠|英冠]][[PFA年度最佳陣容|年度最佳陣容]]」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/page/News/ChampionshipNewsDetail/0,,10794~1640656,00.html |title=Championship team of the year |publisher=[[英格蘭足球聯賽|''football-league.co.uk'']] |date=27 April 2009 |accessdate=27 April 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090430042004/http://www.football-league.co.uk/page/News/ChampionshipNewsDetail/0%2C%2C10794~1640656%2C00.html |archivedate=2009年4月30日 }}</ref>。

====伯明翰城====
2009年6月[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]接納[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]的500萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]出價，此前曾兩度拒絕對方的出價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8113313.stm |title=Cardiff accept Blues' Johnson bid |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=24 June 2009 |accessdate=24 June 2009}}</ref>，羅渣·莊臣於6月25日簽署三年合式正式加盟<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0,,10412~1702843,00.html |title=Johnson Deal Done |publisher=[[伯明翰足球會|''bcfc.com'']] |date=25 June 2009 |accessdate=25 June 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301133716/http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0,,10412~1702843,00.html |archivedate=2012年3月1日 }}</ref>，於球季揭幕日以0-1負於[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]有令人驚喜的處子演出<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/columns/story?id=668102&cc=5739 |title=Wayne's World |publisher=''soccernet.espn.go.com'' |date=16 August 2009 |accessdate=3 April 2010 |archive-date=2012-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021034300/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/columns/story?id=668102&cc=5739 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，季初直到[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]前球隊更保持12場不敗的戰績，是球會在頂級聯賽的一項記錄，而羅渣·莊臣是陣中的主將<ref name="FIFABlues">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/clubfootball/news/newsid=1157547.html |title=Fresh fortunes at St Andrew's |publisher=[[FIFA|''fifa.com'']] |date=15 January 2010 |accessdate=3 April 2010 |archive-date=2010-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100118090630/http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/clubfootball/news/newsid=1157547.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。加盟首個[[2009年至2010年英格蘭超級聯賽|球季]]羅渣·莊臣在全部38場英超聯賽正選上陣，另外在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]亦上陣5仗。

2010年8月29日於作客2-2賽和[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]射入加盟以來首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8946659.stm |title=Bolton 2–2 Birmingham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=29 August 2010 |accessdate=8 September 2010 |archive-date=2011-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110208081615/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8946659.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===狼隊===
[[File:Roger_Johnson.jpg|thumb]]
2011年7月13日羅渣·莊臣轉投[[英超|英超]]球會[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]，簽約四年，轉會費沒有透露，但據報達到700萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，平狼隊歷來付出最高轉會費記錄<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14104644.stm |title=Roger Johnson completes move from Birmingham to Wolves |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-13 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2011-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111110030342/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14104644.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但狼隊表示報導的金額過於誇張<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/News/0,,10307~2391472,00.html |title=Roger And In! |publisher=[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|''wolves.co.uk'']] |date=2011-07-13 |accessdate=2011-08-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816183734/http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/News/0,,10307~2391472,00.html |archivedate=2011-08-16 }}</ref>，其後獲悉其身價僅超越400萬英鎊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.expressandstar.com/sport/wolverhampton-wanderers-fc/2011/07/23/wolves-quids-in-on-roger-johnson-and-jamie-ohara-deals/ |title=Wolves quids in on Roger Johnson and Jamie O'Hara deals |publisher=''expressandstar.com'' |date=2011-07-23 |accessdate=2011-08-15 |archive-date=2016-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017085645/http://www.expressandstar.com/sport/wolverhampton-wanderers-fc/2011/07/23/wolves-quids-in-on-roger-johnson-and-jamie-ohara-deals/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。新球季展開前，羅渣·莊臣獲委任為球隊[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/News/0,,10307~2407703,00.html |title=Johnson The New Captain |publisher=[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|''wolves.co.uk'']] |date=2011-08-02 |accessdate=2011-08-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110808043359/http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/News/0,,10307~2407703,00.html |archivedate=2011-08-08 }}</ref>。

2013年6月24日，要降落[[英甲|英甲]]作賽的[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]宣佈有4名未約滿球員放入可轉會名單，羅渣·莊臣為其中之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.wolves.co.uk/news/article/four-players-transfer-listed-240613-877235.aspx |title=Four Players Transfer Listed |publisher=''wolves.co.uk'' |date=24 June 2013 |accessdate=23 October 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029200240/http://www.wolves.co.uk/news/article/four-players-transfer-listed-240613-877235.aspx |archivedate=2013年10月29日 }}</ref>。

2013年9月16日，[[英冠|英冠]][[谢周三足球俱乐部|錫周三]]完成手續向[[英甲|英甲]][[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]借用羅渣·莊臣，借用期為三個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24107747 |title=Sheffield Wednesday: Roger Johnson signs from Wolves |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=16 September 2013 |accessdate=23 October 2013 |archive-date=2015-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412083914/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24107747 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==私人生活==
羅渣·莊臣與家中的兄弟同為[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]的支持球迷，更曾持有季票長達10年<ref>Moxley, Neil (26 December 2009). [http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1238353/I-Shed-End-loft-says-Birminghams-Chelsea-fan-Roger-Johnson.html "'I keep the Shed End in my loft', says Birmingham's very own Chelsea fan Roger Johnson"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1238353/I-Shed-End-loft-says-Birminghams-Chelsea-fan-Roger-Johnson.html |date=20160820064447 }} ''[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]''. Retrieved 8 September 2010</ref>。2007年6月1日他娶[[模特兒|模特兒]]梅利莎（Melissa）為妻，兩人青梅竹馬，並育有一名女兒波姬（Brooke）<ref>Chamberlain, Zoe (2 May 2010). [http://www.sundaymercury.net/news/midlands-news/2010/05/02/melissa-johnson-i-was-a-wag-before-i-became-blues-roger-johnson-s-wife-66331-26358783/ "Melissa Johnson: I was a WAG before I became Blues' Roger Johnson's wife"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sundaymercury.net/news/midlands-news/2010/05/02/melissa-johnson-i-was-a-wag-before-i-became-blues-roger-johnson-s-wife-66331-26358783/ |date=20120313144415 }} ''[[Sunday_Mercury|Sunday Mercury]]'' (Birmingham). Retrieved 8 September 2010</ref>。

